<p>This endpoint retrieves search results.</p>
<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code class="request">GET /api/v1/search</code></p>
<h3 id='query-parameters'>Query Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Default</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>page</td>
<td><code>Number</code></td>
<td><code>1</code></td>
<td>Intended page</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>limit</td>
<td><code>Number</code></td>
<td><code>20</code></td>
<td>Number of items per page</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>sort</td>
<td><code>String</code></td>
<td><code>createdAt.desc</code></td>
<td>The field to sort on</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>type</td>
<td><code>String</code></td>
<td><code>all</code></td>
<td>Type of the result. It can be one of [<code>question</code> , <code>group</code>, <code>topic</code>, <code>post</code>, <code>user</code>, <code>all</code>]</td>
</tr>
<tr>
